{"id":"410882c29ab17bad2a3c0990cfe4d4c63576f17474dd3243eb00c45368973270","item_id":"52ff0489c5:0","text":"从 RenderMan for Blender 27.0 开始，灯光链接现在有两种模式。第一种模式默认启用，依赖 RenderMan"}
{"id":"117997e4824e330b602bb8215ebe50b2fbd002a7bf89ba7ebb7a605a6bc7a15b","item_id":"52ff0489c5:1","text":"Light Linking Editor（灯光链接编辑器）"}
{"id":"f825a563b8fcc6a1d27d26da824082f4576995815f3c1ad9e63fe3963725e441","item_id":"52ff0489c5:2","text":"。第二种模式使用 Blender 的原生灯光链接工作流（请参阅 Blender 文档，"}
{"id":"fcec91509759ad995c2cd14bcb26b2720993faf61c29d379b270d442d92290eb","item_id":"52ff0489c5:3","text":"此处"}
{"id":"8dc8c0c7da91a62068b2dc6604ec5110ccc2569cbfa285aebb6e6595c220f926","item_id":"52ff0489c5:4","text":"）。请注意，原生工作流要求 Blender 4.1 或更高版本。"}
{"id":"a564cd7d33dec5de034a972b48f0729679b6231eedcbab3de38224797d9718ce","item_id":"52ff0489c5:5","text":"Native Workflow（原生工作流）"}
{"id":"1b94303d5a19d264f235226a657c26517af77f30fbe8d8b387c00a9e05bc7c97","item_id":"52ff0489c5:6","text":"要在 RenderMan for Blender 中使用 Blender 原生灯光链接，请在渲染属性选项卡的 Light Linking 下将 Workflow 设置改为 Blender，如下图所示："}
{"id":"d029f87e3d80f8fd9b1be67c7426b4cc1ff47b4a9d0a8461c826a59d8c5eb6cd","item_id":"52ff0489c5:7","text":"Example（示例）"}
{"id":"c942b14db3e2d613f7d3f274dcee316f604d58c9440253ddb9ef4fc4c85dbc13","item_id":"52ff0489c5:8","text":"这里有一个简单场景，包含 Suzanne 模型、一个环面和一套三点布光设置。"}
{"id":"9375707b2e3ab0ed263736e0815a184c523028fe921191a53fb5fd6b5d905bdf","item_id":"52ff0489c5:9","text":"可以从主光开始进行灯光链接（在本例中它名为 PxrDiskLightShape1）：进入该灯光的对象属性，并在 Shading → Light Linking 下查看。"}
{"id":"2cceeb252f0cf6dc4bd36c84adecc31c33cac5a073d44453336dbca4d08c87ba","item_id":"52ff0489c5:10","text":"创建该集合后，会立即关闭此灯光对该场景中所有对象的照明。"}
{"id":"656361bd6fac3eea19b8e04879a3d5295b43b839f552d795f16570385ea12ab1","item_id":"52ff0489c5:11","text":"现在，如果想把这盏灯与 Suzanne 模型链接起来，可以将 Outliner（大纲视图）中的 Suzanna 对象拖放到灯光链接集合中。"}
{"id":"d6ba3c6db0d79bc0034f020fa24f75e8c74e37d6aeb3f9e1071828e7239b3a7a","item_id":"52ff0489c5:12","text":"这里可以看到，现在这盏灯只照亮 Suzanne 模型。"}
